CSRMESH_DATA_BLOCK_SEND_T Struct Reference
CSRmesh&trade; » Models » Data Model

A block of data, no acknowledgement. Upon receiving a DATA_BLOCK_SEND message, the device passes the DatagramOctets field up to the application for processing.
